data.text:
Urvashi Rautela Faces Backlash Over Paris Video Featuring Controversial Dress

Urvashi Rautela's recent Instagram video from Paris has attracted significant backlash. The clip features her wearing a custom-designed Duena shirt-dress by MaisonJ Simone, which includes images of Mother Mary. The inclusion of religious imagery in the outfit has sparked controversy, leading many viewers to express their anger in the comments section. According to reports, an organisation has urged the Maharashtra government to take action against Rautela, demanding that she face charges for offending religious sentiments. In response, the actress posted a clarification note on social media, and an apology from Urvashi was reportedly conveyed through her spokesperson. On the work front, Urvashi is currently receiving praise for her performance in Ghuspaithiya.

35 views | 5 hours ago

Pakistani Singer Ali Zafar Announces 1 Million Reward for Gold Medalist Arshad Nadeem

Pakistan is bustling with celebration after Arshad Nadeem’s remarkable gold medal win. Nadeem achieved a record-breaking throw of 92.97 meters, setting social media abuzz with congratulatory messages for the country’s latest sports hero. The praise has poured in from many cricketers and actors, who have lauded Nadeem’s outstanding performance. In addition, Ali Zafar has announced a cash reward of PKR 1 million for Nadeem and has called for the establishment of a sports academy in his honor. Zafar shared a video of Nadeem’s throw on social media and reiterated his call for a hero’s welcome. Actress Mahira Khan also joined in the celebrations by posting about the ‘hero’ Arshad Nadeem.

279 views | 3 days ago

Bollywood Fraternity Unites In Solidarity For Vinesh Phogat After Her Disqualification At Paris Olympics

The world of Bollywood stands together in support of Indian wrestling sensation Vinesh Phogat following her shocking disqualification at the Paris Olympics. Watch as your favorite stars express their heartfelt messages and rally behind Vinesh during this challenging time. Witness the power of unity and the spirit of sportsmanship as the entire film industry sends their love and encouragement to our champion.

224 views | 4 days ago

Janhvi Kapoor and Orry's Hilarious Video Goes Viral; Shanaya Compares Them to 'Kim & North'

Orhan Awatramani’s latest video has become a social media sensation. The clip features Janhvi in a bathroom while Orry dances around her, showing off his goofy moves. The video has quickly turned into a laugh riot online, drawing widespread attention. Janhvi and Orry's close friend, Shanaya, couldn't resist reacting to the video, even comparing the duo to Kim Kardashian and her daughter North. This isn’t the first time Orry has shared such content; he frequently posts hilarious videos and pictures with his BFF, Janhvi. Janhvi Kapoor was last seen in Sudhanshu Saria's film Ulajh, and she is currently making headlines for her recently released song "Dheere Dheere" from the movie Devara.
